title: I Began Selling Jars from Naruto World - Novel Updates

description:
Crossing over to the world of Naruto with the Transaction System.

Shen Mo travelled across all heavens to sell jars as a travelling merchant.

Tsunade: Don’t obstruct me Shizune, today I must pull a Life Token!

Uchiha Sasuke: Can I really become stronger by opening jars? Use my entire family fortune to buy jars, I must surpass that man!

Gol D. Roger: Why isn’t everyone going to seek my buried treasure but went to purchase jars instead?

Misaka Mikoto: One side goes through, I will finish opening these jars then I will thoroughly flatten you!

Uchiha Itachi: My foolish otouto, I opened more jars than you.

……

Shen Mo is looking at the crazily cash recharging numerous protagonists with helpless expression… I initially just wanted to earn enough money to buy Ikaros, that’s all.>
